    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you can, add the game to your wishlist, it helps us a lot! &lt;3</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Home decoration simulator game. The game is still in the development phase, but can already be purchased in advance.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302620/extras/04c4e623fc1d793fc34ce1a3b1a1178c.poster.avif?t=1766839092\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302620/extras/04c4e623fc1d793fc34ce1a3b1a1178c.webm?t=1766839092\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302620/extras/04c4e623fc1d793fc34ce1a3b1a1178c.mp4?t=1766839092\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >home decor:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Decorate your home as you wish with various objects for the kitchen, living room, bedroom, bathroom, garden, and decoration.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302620/extras/00c7a687830f6d6d2b955d916503ffc3.poster.avif?t=1766839092\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302620/extras/00c7a687830f6d6d2b955d916503ffc3.webm?t=1766839092\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302620/extras/00c7a687830f6d6d2b955d916503ffc3.mp4?t=1766839092\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302620/extras/6615c89ded58ad828c857faf18fd4d9b.poster.avif?t=1766839092\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302620/extras/6615c89ded58ad828c857faf18fd4d9b.webm?t=1766839092\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302620/extras/6615c89ded58ad828c857faf18fd4d9b.mp4?t=1766839092\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Assemble the house creatively, there are several objects.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302620/extras/3c5d324c5923255159024d060e1cd3fe.poster.avif?t=1766839092\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302620/extras/3c5d324c5923255159024d060e1cd3fe.webm?t=1766839092\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302620/extras/3c5d324c5923255159024d060e1cd3fe.mp4?t=1766839092\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Most objects have animation on it, it is possible to swap animate objects.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302620/extras/515f63aceac50c1dfa496c6f57d9841b.poster.avif?t=1766839092\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302620/extras/515f63aceac50c1dfa496c6f57d9841b.webm?t=1766839092\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302620/extras/515f63aceac50c1dfa496c6f57d9841b.mp4?t=1766839092\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302620/extras/dd662a14bf34f3a88964d8effa05524c.poster.avif?t=1766839092\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302620/extras/dd662a14bf34f3a88964d8effa05524c.webm?t=1766839092\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302620/extras/dd662a14bf34f3a88964d8effa05524c.mp4?t=1766839092\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The kitchen speaker plays several songs, just add it to the scene and press play, when you delete it from the house it stops playing, or when you press the stop command.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you like design, interior design, decoration, decorating environments, this game is ideal for you.</p></li></ul>",
